    "The advantage of this rescaling is that Euclidean space is obtained as a continuous limit as κ → 0.",
    "In the rescaled model, gyrovectorspace addition and scalar product become",
    "for p, q ∈ D d κ.",
    "The exponential map in the direction of a tangent vector v ∈ T p can then be written as",
    "for p ∈ D d κ, see Ganea et al. (2018b)."
